data.description: **Home has 4 true bedrooms** Welcome to this immaculate 4-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, 3-car garage home nestled on a sprawling corner lot with the essence of great pride in ownership. This meticulously maintained property has an open-concept living space, updated with brand new laminate flooring. Enjoy the AC or the heated garage for comfort in all seasons and convenience for storage. The spacious kitchen boasts lots of counter-space and a large breakfast bar making it an ideal space for gatherings. Don't miss the backyard oasis. The lush green grass, a tranquil waterfall cascading into a pond, and a charming bar area under the gazebo with warm string lights that create a magical ambiance during evenings - perfect for outdoor entertainment. There is also a RV gate with room to park your toys, a storage shed and a dog run!
